    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>In 2020, I want to work on a new electronics project involving solar.  I think a durable, outdoor solar lamp would be interesting.  It would need a solar panel,
a charge controller, a battery, and a lamp.  I want to make a yard lamp that runs all night using energy it acquired charging all day.  It seems doable, if I
can find the parts necessary and the information about the electronics.</p>

<!-- more -->


<p>I want to build the project in some computer-aided design program first, confirm that the components are compatible and sized properly, then build the board and
installation box on my bench.</p>

<p>I&#8217;ll update this page as I find he right parts.</p>

